entries.femaleVariant: One thing I know like I know my own name – you do not poke around strangers' coolboxes. Best case scenario, you find a half-gallon jug of rancid milk, worst--
Who?
Motherfucker up a satmast. That's Rache Bartmoss!
I'd recognize that mug anywhere. Wanted posters all over town back in twenty-twenty. Public enemy number one, dead or alive… Half the city was on the hunt.
Poor bastard. Ended up here as a dead rat in a coolbox... Till some circuit blew and he thawed like so much meat.
Ugh... Fuck a dogdoll…
The Rache Bartmoss?!
The Bartmoss? DataKrash RABID Bartmoss? Guy who trashed the first Net?
Rache who?
Whaddaya mean, "Rache who?" Bartmoss, for shit's sake! Gonk who fuckin' trashed the first net?
Well, it wasn't his uncle. Yeah, yeah, him!
Uh-huh. Yeah, 'bout twenty years back, judgin' by the stench. Well, stood about as much as I can, gotta go.
Hold up, hold up! Gotta be some electronics in here. First-Net relics, almost crank-powered? Be a shame just to leave it.
I'll think about it.
Even if there is, it's bound to be bunk.
Need to think about it.
entries.maleVariant: Nah, need to think about it.

entries.femaleVariant: Even if there is, it's bound to be bunk.
Bound to be? Wouldn't be so sure. Only one way to find out.
Said the gonk who missed the shuttle. C'mon, look inside.
Well, well... an SGI Tech "Elysla." Best cyberdeck in its class.
Hm... whadda we got here? Looks like... a box.
You're a fuckin' box. Try cyberdeck.
See? Worth gettin' a little rot on your hands sometimes.
Hey! One of the Afterlife's denizens – Nix? Could prolly pull some data from this, don'tcha think?
'Ey! Just thinkin' – cat at the Afterlife, goes by Nix… Looked like somebody who'd know legacy tech.
Chat 'im up, see what happens… Could end up pullin' somethin' from it.
Aaah, not so sure. Near came to blows last time we had some biz.
entries.maleVariant: Pss, not so sure. Near came to blows last time we had some biz.

entries.femaleVariant: Yadda yadda. Soon as he hears it's Bartmoss tech, he'll piss himself silly. You'll see.
DataKrash? RABIDs? No pings? Jesus, what'm I doin' here, who are you, even…?
Couldn't hurt to ask.
[Close] That stench...
[Open]
[Open]
[Take cyberdeck]
